{"tid":6311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港羽毛球錦標賽　伍家朗首度奪冠","createTime":"2016-11-27T09:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T10:12:31.000Z","uid":8883,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70f3942a9392776a9d913a954f77db0af5e8f24d","tid":6311,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"「 香港公開羽毛球錦標賽」今日（27日）在香港體育館上演決賽，22歲的伍家朗，以局數2:1擊敗同為22歲的印度球手山米亞，首次在主場奪得這項賽事男單冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n伍家朗昨日以2：0擊退35歲師兄胡贇，晉身決賽，已為香港羽壇在香港站創歷史，首奪男單決賽席位，最後勝出決賽，更是再進一步，為港隊和自己開創紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n世界排名43的山米亞昨日爆冷以2：0意外賽果擊敗今屆賽事三號種子丹麥的約根森，殺入決賽。<br />\n<br />\n伍家朗今天在決賽首局勝21:14，山米亞以10:21追回一局，到第三局，伍家朗以21:11勝出，奪得男單冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n伍家朗上屆在這項香港公開賽，曾擊敗中國的林丹，而備受注目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/sport/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%BE%BD%E6%AF%9B%E7%90%83%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%99%E8%B3%BD-%E4%BC%8D%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%97%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25BE%25BD%25E6%25AF%259B%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25B3%25BD-%25E4%25BC%258D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0%2F&d=B3wWFzDYCiY6GGcomhzFmsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=892b0704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25BE%25BD%25E6%25AF%259B%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25B3%25BD-%25E4%25BC%258D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0%2F&h=670a7a3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/sport/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%BE%BD%E6%AF%9B%E7%90%83%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%99%E8%B3%BD-%E4%BC%8D%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%97%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0/</a>"},{"pid":"8639335ed832260239b07889488bd53019396f3f","tid":6311,"uid":26803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1651b22b0c2c20758c191ec2d